
# Interactive component

## New York City Precinct Map of Crimes in 2020

This map contains hate crimes data of different precincts in New York City in 2020. In this interactive map, you can see 8 kinds of statistics, "TOTAL", "ASSAULT",  "DRUGS", "WEAPONS", "FELONY", "MPL", "ROBBERY" and "HATE". When mousing over the region of this precinct, these statistics of specific precinct will show up to help you quickly know the safety situation in this area. As discussed in **5.1.3**, we found 6 most numerous crimes from 2006 to 2021. In this map, ASSAULT denotes ***ASSAULT 3 & RELATED OFFENSES***. DRUGS denotes ***DANGEROUS DRUGS***. WEAPONS denotes ***DANGEROUS WEAPONS***. FELONY denotes ***FELONY ASSAULT***. MPL denotes ***MISCELLANEOUS PENAL LAW***. ROBBERY denotes ***ROBBERY***. HATE denotes the number of hate crimes cases in NYPD_Hate_Crimes.csv.
